OL,6,FBut assuming a 50-50 gender split at
OL,7,FSaturday's game, statistically 324 men
OL,8,Fand 19 women in Swindon's County
OL,9,FGround would have been affected by the
OL,10,Fkit clash.
OL,12,FTheir view of the game could have
OL,13,Flooked more like this:
OL,15,FThe charity Colour Blind Awareness
OL,16,Fsaid it's "very disappointing to see a
OL,17,Fcolour-blind kit clash so early in the
OL,18,Fnew season."
