OL,3,CWalsall football kit confusion for
OL,4,Ccolour-blind fans
OL,6,FIt pointed out: "The FA/UEFA
OL,7,Fguidelines 'Colour Blindness in
OL,8,FFootball' were issued in 2017 and
OL,9,Fclearly show all-red kits are
OL,10,Fdifficult to distinguish from all-
OL,11,Fblack kits for large numbers of colour-
OL,12,Fblind people."
OL,14,FAn update to the EFL's colour
OL,15,Fblindness kit clash policy in 2022
OL,16,Fmeant home teams can wear their away
OL,17,For third kit to make it easier for
OL,18,Fcolour-blind fans to differentiate
OL,19,Fbetween teams.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
