OL,3,CWalsall football kit confusion for
OL,4,Ccolour-blind fans
OL,6,FIt also allowed clubs to 'mix and
OL,7,Fmatch' elements of kits - such as
OL,8,Fwearing shorts which aren't the same
OL,9,Fcolour as their shirts.
OL,11,FThe EFL said it now plays an active
OL,12,Frole in helping spot potential kit
OL,13,Fclashes but said this is "guidance
OL,14,Frather than a mandatory requirement"
OL,15,Ffor clubs.
OL,17,FColour Blind Awareness said "it's now
OL,18,Fup to clubs to take responsibility for
OL,19,Ftheir own actions and how their
OL,20,Fdecisions affected their fans, players
OL,21,Fand sponsors."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
