OL,3,CWalsall football kit confusion for
OL,4,Ccolour-blind fans
OL,6,FThe charity said 5% of elite male
OL,7,Ffootballers are colour-blind, roughly
OL,8,Fequating to one in every squad.
OL,10,FIt said kit clashes can have an effect
OL,11,Fon players' performance.
OL,13,FIt said: "We can't understand why
OL,14,FWalsall's kit supplier, Macron (which
OL,15,Fhas received training from us in how
OL,16,Fto avoid this) has designed an all-
OL,17,Fblack kit with red logos/branding
OL,18,Fmaking their own and the club's logos
OL,19,Fas well as the main kit sponsor's name
OL,20,F(Poundland) practically invisible to a
OL,21,Flarge number of colour blind people."
